{"tid":726077,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【跨國團聚】5歲女走失獲美夫妻收養 13年後與親生父母重逢","createTime":"2018-07-02T06:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T16:12:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":76,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e5501801df75cc5c3fa47e7d86ba39ca0a58e5da","tid":726077,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:10:37.000Z","msg":"漫漫回家路！7月1日，廣州白雲機場，從美國趕來的中鳳敏見到了自己的親生父母，相見那一刻，她和父親緊緊抱在一起。這條重逢的路，這對父女走了13年。<br />\n<br />\n不知是否受獲第89屆奧斯卡六項奧斯卡提名、由真人真事改編《漫漫回家路》（Lion）影響，今年4月，中鳳敏通過網絡、媒體發佈尋親訊息：5歲時，她在廣東中山市東鳳鎮走失，被福利院起名「中鳳敏」，並於2012年被一對美國夫妻收養，今年18歲的她已被美國名校錄取。<br />\n<br />\n中鳳敏的尋親訊息被在佛山市順德區居住的梁華看到，經過相關信息比對，他發現「中鳳敏」和失散多年的女兒梁晶浪相似。經過經過近2個月的短訊交流、DNA比對，終於確認中鳳敏就是梁華的女兒梁晶浪。<br />\n<br />\n原來，2005年梁華在順德容桂打工，居住在員工宿舍，他的弟弟則在格蘭仕打工，租住在中山東鳳鎮的一間出租屋內。當年5月，學校放假，梁華把女兒梁晶浪從老家接到順德，由於員工宿舍不允許居住，他就把女兒送到弟弟的住所，殊不知5月20日上午晴天，中午卻突然傾盆大雨，梁晶浪自此失蹤。13年來，梁華尋訪各地，卻始終難覓女兒蹤影。<br />\n<br />\n昨日中午，中鳳敏（即梁晶浪）抵達廣州白雲機場，她靠在13年未見的父親梁華懷裏，並給父親愛的親吻，還沒反應過來的梁華眼睛裏泛着淚光。他緊緊抱着13年未見的女兒梁晶浪走出機場。而在順德家中，門口佈滿氣球，掛着橫幅，氣球上印着I LOVE YOU，橫幅上用中英文寫着歡迎她回家。讓梁華感到欣慰的是，不僅與女兒重逢，女兒還是美國名校伊利諾伊大學香檳分校的學霸。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/02/141024_dbd3b531daa2898e6297ff07221f7067.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2F141024_dbd3b531daa2898e6297ff07221f7067.png&h=7951ad87&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/02/141024_65f221fcf1ba552307b2117a7d5417e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2F141024_65f221fcf1ba552307b2117a7d5417e0.png&h=80180c6c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/02/141025_65f221fcf1ba552307b2117a7d5417e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2F141025_65f221fcf1ba552307b2117a7d5417e0.png&h=680f9ccd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180702/58389045\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180702%2F58389045&d=uLK1R3VyKD4%2BN24X34HBUsP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=3c255e36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180702%2F58389045&h=0ff2d0a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180702/58389045</a>"},{"pid":"806b88f498811fbd06496761b464e0dd73bd6fe0","tid":726077,"uid":9732,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:12:30.000Z","msg":"好嘔心"},{"pid":"a3a490190f3f633ee192d79c265408af582b954e","tid":726077,"uid":39786,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:13:41.000Z","msg":"唔洗驗DNA, 一睇就知係兩父女 －＿－"},{"pid":"97c5f34473674c5cfd45b1fc32316d98c29522bf","tid":726077,"uid":29702,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:15:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06fa43800050ed459984637f9e724dd53f63ed22","tid":726077,"uid":29702,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:15:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8df51842d5c553f6edadcb1e063c006b90d363b0","tid":726077,"uid":42735,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:17:24.000Z","msg":"佢唔係美國人既話佢老豆老母撚會認返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"875770b47b6f2c58c1d9caa650d29781cfa805f1","tid":726077,"uid":29702,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:21:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a09324be209baf08ac7011270b299bce083c9fb","tid":726077,"uid":35014,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:27:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a3033607ed358db8e554401c2c91c62c1bf2f72","tid":726077,"uid":37005,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:30:26.000Z","msg":"大陸咩正面嘅新聞都覺得係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" c